    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/2093b00a3bc377de7ea506853bd39a11.avif?t=1732105463\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>在保护区最初开放时，莱顿湖区和赫希费尔登狩猎保护区共有10个物种可狩猎，梅德韦泰嘉国家公园另增了4个新物种，乌尔霍加热带稀树草原增加了7个，费南多自然公园增加了6个。在那之后，保护区又增加了4个新物种，其中就包括南非剑羚、黑额黑雁等。随着生态环境的变迁，新的物种出现了……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >狮子：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/d35d60f41d90298bc6d1f6c0cc483b1b.poster.avif?t=1732105463\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/d35d60f41d90298bc6d1f6c0cc483b1b.webm?t=1732105463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/d35d60f41d90298bc6d1f6c0cc483b1b.mp4?t=1732105463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>随着乌尔霍加热带稀树草原的不断繁盛，祖父尼亚布觉得是时候让位于食物链顶端的百兽之王狮子回到故乡了。作为人类世界中荣耀和尊贵的象征，狮子是仅次于老虎的第二大猫科动物。在狩猎过程中，它们健硕躯体上密布的肌肉会对子弹的着弹点和穿透力造成限制。回到乌尔霍加热带稀树草原的狮子可谓是如鱼得水，它们可不会轻易放过自己领地上的猎物。深入野外狩猎丛林之王，在保持行事果决的同时你还需要多一分智慧。 <br><br><strong>从丛林之王的口中脱险：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/f6804fa26707b58e3b9516bed08d8dc0.avif?t=1732105463\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>狮子偏好从目标身后发动进攻，咬住对方脖子，一击毙命。在应对体型较小的猎物时，他们会显得更加从容，且动作迅猛。乌尔霍加热带稀树草原上的狮子并不吃人，不过它们会袭击任何胆敢入侵它们领地的人类。只要与它们保持距离，你就不会被盯上。当你和这样一个巨兽碰个正着时候一定要镇定行事，稍有差错就会有生命危险…… <br><br><strong>感官和种间关系：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/886c9c8eb171f5d7c31e462e2e8326ce.poster.avif?t=1732105463\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/886c9c8eb171f5d7c31e462e2e8326ce.webm?t=1732105463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/886c9c8eb171f5d7c31e462e2e8326ce.mp4?t=1732105463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>狮子这个顶级掠食者可不是徒有虚名。除了拥有着开阔的视野和敏锐的洞察力之外，它们具备着非同一般嗅觉和听力。想要出其不意地捕获这些巨兽那可不简单。  <br><br><strong>变种：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/92132c5798dad296751819017dc3bc58.poster.avif?t=1732105463\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/92132c5798dad296751819017dc3bc58.webm?t=1732105463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011280/extras/92132c5798dad296751819017dc3bc58.mp4?t=1732105463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>乌尔霍加热带稀树草原上的狮子站立的时候身高超过1米，据说它们有5个毛色。最常见的是标准的浅褐色，几名幸运的猎人发现了拥有更多其他独特毛色的狮子。那么问题来了：你有能力抓到一只吗？",
